    "shortDescription": "<p>A globe of shimmering force encloses a creature, provided the creature is small enough to fit within the diameter of the sphere.</p><p>The sphere contains its subject for the spell's duration. The sphere functions as a <i>Wall of Force</i>, except that it can be negated by dispel magic. A subject inside the sphere can breathe normally.</p><p>The sphere cannot be physically moved either by people outside it or by the struggles of those within.</p>"
